The perpetrator believed that he was taking revenge on a man who sexually abused a loved one.
The police duly investigated the case and later tracked down the attacker.
The man was originally sentenced to a minimum of eight years in prison.
However, later the verdict changed fundamentally, to the amazement of Christopheros' family.
