And journalists are being persecuted and killed, as in the case of Ruben Espinoso, who was murdered along with four women in an apartment in Mexico City in 2015, three months after fleeing Veracruza.
For those who have decided to stay and not give up their job, every day is a big risk.
Ibarra, who wanted to be a poet one day, admits that writing about drugs scares him.
